::Battera::

She sat in her new quaters and waited.  She looked about.  It still 
looked like a nicely decorated cell to her.  She felt caged. She got 
up and walked around the room for a bit.  She decided to get to know 
these bots a bit better.  Who knows, it might prove a useful 
connection to have in the future.  She went to the door, but it 
didn't open. She looked around and saw the panel on the side of the 
door. "Ok, if your head wasn't attached, you'd have flown off and 
left it long ago." She pressed the button and the doors opened.  She 
walked down the hall and looked about.  She was hoping to run into 
Chardate.  She had a few questions and was hoping to get some answers.
